OL,3,CFour arrested after painkillers and
OL,4,Csedatives go missing from pharmacy
OL,6,FFour people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fpainkillers and sedatives went missing
OL,8,Ffrom a pharmacy.
OL,10,FThe arrests are part of an ongoing
OL,11,Fpolice investigation into the illegal
OL,12,Fsale of prescription-only drugs.JAvon
OL,13,Fand Somerset Police were alerted after
OL,14,Fa pharmacy's audit revealed
OL,15,Fpainkillers and sedatives were
OL,16,Fmissing.JOfficers obtained warrants
OL,17,Fand searched several home addresses in
OL,18,FYeovil earlier this month. A variety
OL,19,Fof prescription-only medications were
OL,20,Fseized.
