OL,9,Fproduct with intent to supply, not in
OL,10,Faccordance with a prescription.
OL,11,FAnother man, aged in his thirties, and
OL,12,Fa woman in her fifties were arrested
OL,13,Fon suspicion of conspiring to sell/
OL,14,Fsupply prescription-only medicine not
OL,15,Fin accordance with a prescription.JAll
OL,16,Ffour were later released on bail
OL,17,Fpending further enquiries and the
OL,18,Finvestigation continues.JEast Somerset
OL,19,FArea Commander Chief Inspector Andy
OL,20,FPritchard said: "The sale of
OL,21,Fprescription-only drugs without an
OL,22,Fappropriate prescription is an offence
OL,23,Fover and above the inherent risk of
OL,24,Ftaking a drug without the right
OL,25,Fmedical assessment.
